items.title: Republican congressman hospitalized after car accident, sources say
items.description: Rep. Jim Baird hospitalized after car accident, reported in stable condition. Indiana Republican congressman remains responsive following the incident...

items.title: Republicans rally behind Trump's military strike to arrest Maduro as Democrats sound alarm: poll
items.description: A new poll reveals a sharp partisan divide over Trump's military operation leading to the capture of Venezuelan leader Nicholas Maduro on drug traffic...

items.title: National Rifle Association sues its charitable foundation, alleging takeover by 'disgruntled' ex-board members
items.description: Former NRA directors accused of seizing control of charitable foundation to compete with gun rights group after losing board power amid scandals.

items.title: Mamdani admits he has no federal security clearance after claiming he was 'briefed' on Venezuela raid
items.description: NYC Mayor Zohran Mamdani admitted he lacks security clearance after saying he was "briefed" on Nicolas Maduro's capture this weekend.

items.title: House GOP Rep Doug LaMalfa dead at 65
items.description: California Congressman Doug LaMalfa has passed away at age 65.
